    <preface>
      <p><b>OVERSEAS OPERATIONS (SERVICE PERSONNEL AND VETERANS) ACT 2021</b></p>
      <p><span style="color:#000000">EXPLANATORY NOTES</span></p>
    </preface>
    <mainBody>
      <toc>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2021/23/notes" level="1"><inline name="tocHeading">The whole Explanatory Note</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2021/23/notes/section/1" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Overview of the Act</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2021/23/notes/section/2" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Policy and legal background</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2021/23/notes/section/3" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Territorial extent and application</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2021/23/notes/section/4" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Commentary on provisions of Act</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_4" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Part 1: Restrictions on prosecution for certain offences</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_4" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Presumption against prosecution</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_4" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Consent to prosecution</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_4" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Part 2: Limitation Periods</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_4" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Part 3: General</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2021/23/notes/section/5" level="2"><inline name="tocHeading">Commencement</inline></tocItem>
